ero-overlay" style="background:transparent;opacity:0.2"></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1675759363835" class="gf_row gf_row-fluid gf_row-no-padding" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1675759363835" style="display: block;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675759363907" data-id="1675759363907"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675759985184" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675759985184"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Parker</h1></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1680594068361" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1680594068361"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1680594068342" data-id="1680594068342"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675760058653" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675760058653"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><font color="#000000">Parker is probably the most famous pen brand on the planet, catering for all budgets and tastes, and we have a wide range of Parker Pens to suit any tastes and budget. The Duofold is its most prestigious Parker pen and dates from the 1920s, while the Parker 51, with its unusual hooded nib, was described as 'the pen from another planet'. The Parker Jotter in particular is one of the most recognisable writing instruments there is, and Parker Quink is virtually synonymous with ink.</font></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1675767368661" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1675767368661" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: block; flex-wrap: unset; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767368623" data-id="1675767368623" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767519795" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767519795" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><a href="https://cultpens.com/collections/parker-jotter" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/2fbb9c52-cd71-41cc-b4d6-ed8491707fd9/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/parker-tile-001.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1556" height="1000" natural-width="1556" natural-height="1000" style="" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770662767" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675770662767"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="https://cultpens.com/collections/parker-jotter" class="">Parker Jotter</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770760680" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770760680"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>The Parker Jotter pen is familiar to one and all. Its simple, classic design has stood the test of time and now Parker have given it a bit of a makeover which can only add to its appeal.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">The plastic barrel is now stainless steel, the pocket clip has been upgraded and there are new colours to choose from.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767384572" data-id="1675767384572" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767638977" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767638977" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><a href="https://cultpens.com/collections/parker-im" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/4207d5cc-0b33-42b6-97a9-e0a5e7ce845d/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/parker-tile-002.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1556" height="1000" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1556" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770684406" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675770684406"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="https://cultpens.com/collections/parker-im" class="">Parker IM</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770879686" class="element-wrap" data